# Collaborative documents (shared-document)

> Merit-based collaborative editing: official block text, proposed variants, voting with заслуги, manual vs auto apply. PRD: `docs/prd/shared-document/`.

---

## Concept

- **Document** (`documents`): belongs to a **community** (`communityId`). Types: `imageOfFuture` (one per community — ОБ), `description` (one per project community), `custom` (only when `documentsMode === 'all'`; no create API yet).
- **Sections → blocks**: embedded in the document. Each **block** has stable `id`, `officialContent`, `blockType`, optional `currentWaveStartedAt`, `proposalsLocked`, edit metadata (`officialContentReason`: `initial` | `vote` | `admin`).
- **Variant** (`document_block_variants`): proposed alternative for one block; `status`: `open` → `closed-winner` / `closed-not-winner` → `applied`; `withdrawn` if author retracts. **Multiple open variants per block from different authors are allowed** (no one-variant-per-user limit).
- **Votes**: reuse **`Vote`** with `targetType === 'document-variant'` or `'document-block-official'` (`targetId` = variant id or `{docId}::{blockId}`).

---

## Community settings

| Setting | Role |
|---------|------|
| `documentsMode` | `'off'` \| `'visionOrDescriptionOnly'` \| `'all'` |
| `documentCreators` | `'admins'` \| `'members'` — who may propose (custom docs + members mode) |
| `documentVariantCost` | Proposal fee (null → use `postCost`) |
| `documentVotingDurationHours` | Default wave length copied to new official docs |
| `documentDefaultMode` | `'manual'` \| `'auto'` — copied to new official docs |

**Not exposed in UI:** `documentAutoApplyTimerHours` exists in schema/migration defaults but is **unused** by finalize/auto-apply (auto-apply runs immediately after wave close when `mode === 'auto'`).

New communities default `documentsMode: 'visionOrDescriptionOnly'`.

---

## Apply modes (`MeriterDocument.mode`)

| Mode | After wave finalize (positive winner) |
|------|----------------------------------------|
| **`manual`** | `document_variant_won` notification; lead/author applies via `applyVotingWinner` or `applyOpenAsAdmin` |
| **`auto`** | `tryAutoApplyWinner` → `applyVariantToOfficial` as `MERITER_DOCUMENT_AUTO_APPLY_USER_ID` |

`applyVotingWinner` rejected when `mode !== 'manual'`.

Also: `applyOfficialVotingWinner` (keep official text, close wave), `applyAdminOverride` (direct official text), `applyOpenAsAdmin` (apply open variant without vote outcome).

---

## Voting waves and cron

- **Wave anchor:** first `proposeVariant` on a block sets `currentWaveStartedAt` and resets `officialRating`.
- **Open window:** `now <= start + document.votingDurationHours` (per-document hours after bootstrap).
- **Finalize:** `finalizeExpiredWaveOnBlock` — rank open variants vs block `officialRating`; positive winner → `closed-winner`; else all `closed-not-winner`; Mongo lock per block.
- **Cron:** `DocumentWaveCronService` `*/5 * * * *` → `runPeriodicWaveSweep()`.
- **On propose:** pre-finalize elapsed waves on that block.

---

## Economics

- **Propose:** fee `document_variant_proposal` (quota/wallet → global burn).
- **Max variant body:** 5000 chars after sanitize.
- **Vote:** comment **required** for document targets in **all** communities.

---

## Mirror to legacy fields (ОБ / description)

- **`mirrorOfficialTextToCommunityIfApplicable`** updates `Community.futureVisionText` (OB) or `description` (project) from `concatOfficialPlainText` + `stripHtmlForMirror` (block types lost in mirror — lists become plain lines).
- **OB hub post:** same mirror path calls `PublicationService.updateFutureVisionPostContent` on `future-vision` hub.
- **Direct edit forbidden:** `CommunityService.updateCommunity` **rejects** `futureVisionText` / `futureVisionDocumentSeed` — ОБ must be edited only via collaborative document. Tags/cover still updatable on community.
- **Create flows (canonical):** `futureVisionText` (plain mirror) + **`futureVisionDocumentSeed`** (structured sections) on community create — used by `CommunityForm`, `CreateTeamDialog`, `CreateProjectForm` (`newCommunity`). Bootstrap seeds OB document from seed.

---

## Future Visions feed display

- **`communities.getFutureVisions`** batch-loads `imageOfFuture` sections via `getOfficialByCommunities`.
- **Web:** `FutureVisionCard` / `CommunityHeroCard` use **`DocumentOfficialPreview`** when sections present; fallback **`CollapsibleRichPreview`** from plain `futureVisionText`.
- **Search (client):** `FutureVisionFeed` matches name, mirror text, and **`documentSectionsSearchPlainText(sections)`**.
- **Public read:** feed is public; document pages require auth but **any logged-in user** may read documents (no membership gate on read).

---

## Hub / documents entry UX

- **No OB document** on MVP hubs: `future-vision`, `marathon-of-good`, `team-projects`.
- **Community hub «Документы» link:** visible only to **community members** (`lead`/`participant`) when `documentsMode !== 'off'`. ОБ preview on hero / future-visions feed remains visible to everyone.
- **Edit ОБ:** settings `?edit=futureVision` redirects to `/documents` list; edit mode in `CommunityForm` shows link to collaborative document only.

---

## Variant references (§17)

Up to 10 links: `url` (http/https, ≤2000), `summary` (≤280, required), optional `stance` (`pro` | `con`). Stay on variant after apply.

---

## Block history (§19)

`block.editHistory` on each `officialContent` change: `previousContent`, `changedBy`, `changedAt`, `reason`, optional `variantId`.

---

## Document structure

- **Who:** lead, document author, superadmin (`assertCanEditDocumentStructure` / `assertCanManageDocument`).
- **tRPC `documents`:** `addSection`, `updateSection`, `removeSection`, `addBlock`, `updateBlock`, `removeBlock`, `reorderBlocks`.
- **Guards:** cannot remove sole section/block; non-empty official removal needs `confirmLossOfOfficial: true`; open variants on removed blocks → `withdrawn`; OB/description re-mirror after structure change.
- **Web:** structure mode toggle, dnd reorder, mobile `BottomActionSheet` for propose/vote/admin.

---

## Server HTML

`sanitizeDocumentHtml` on `propose` and `applyAdminOverride`; aligned with web `DocumentRichContent` (DOMPurify).

---

## tRPC surface

### `documents` (all `protectedProcedure`)

| Procedure | Notes |
|-----------|--------|
| `listByCommunity`, `getById`, `getOfficialByType` | Read; lazy `ensureOfficialDocumentsForCommunity` |
| `updateMeta` | Title (custom only), mode, hours, cost, allowDownvotes |
| `applyAdminOverride` | Direct official text |
| Structure mutations | Optional `expectedUpdatedAt` concurrency |

### `documentVariants`

| Procedure | Notes |
|-----------|--------|
| `listByBlock`, `getBlockVotingPanel`, `getBlockGovernanceHistory` | |
| `propose`, `withdraw` | |
| `applyVotingWinner`, `applyOfficialVotingWinner`, `applyOpenAsAdmin` | |
| `closeVotingWaveOnBlock`, `deleteVariant` | |

### `votes`

`create` / `createWithComment` with `document-variant` or `document-block-official`.

---

## Web routes

- `/meriter/communities/[id]/documents` — list (members; auth required)
- `/meriter/communities/[id]/documents/[documentId]` — canvas; deep link `#block-{blockId}` (notifications)
- `routes.communityDocumentBlock(communityId, documentId, blockId)`

---

## Notifications

| Type | When |
|------|------|
| `document_variant_proposed` | New variant (leads + document author, not proposer) |
| `document_variant_not_selected` | Lost after apply / wave / admin override |
| `document_variant_won` | `closed-winner` after finalize (positive rating) |
| `document_variant_applied` | Applied to official |
| `document_block_admin_override` | Admin override on block |

Redirect: `/meriter/communities/{communityId}/documents/{documentId}` + `#block-{blockId}` when metadata includes `blockId`.

---

## Deploy / migration

- **`CollaborativeDocumentsMigrationService`** runs on **every API startup** (`onModuleInit`), revision-gated (`COLLABORATIVE_DOCUMENTS_MIGRATION_REVISION`).
- **Production:** do **not** set `MERITER_MANUAL_COLLABORATIVE_DOCUMENTS_MIGRATION=1` (disables auto-run).
- **Manual dry-run:** `pnpm --filter @meriter/api migrate:collaborative-documents:dry`.

---

## MVP scope notes

- **In scope:** OB + project description docs, variants, waves, canvas UX, OB feed sync, notifications, member-only documents hub link.
- **Out of scope (backlog):** `documentsMode: 'all'`, custom document create UI, desktop side rail (removed/unshipped).

